00:35:13,981 --> 00:35:15,896
I could help
with Luna, too.

880
00:35:15,939 --> 00:35:17,158
♪♪

881
00:35:17,202 --> 00:35:18,377
Yeah, no, scratch that.

882
00:35:18,420 --> 00:35:19,378
Next round's on me,
