00:40:02,748 --> 00:40:04,837
No, but ask me.

974
00:40:04,880 --> 00:40:07,274
I have a speech.

975
00:40:07,317 --> 00:40:09,189
Oh. Okay.

976
00:40:09,232 --> 00:40:10,799
Nick,
what are you doing here?

977
00:40:10,843 --> 00:40:12,497
