1024
00:42:15,663 --> 00:42:19,972
♪♪

1025
00:42:20,015 --> 00:42:21,321
What?

1026
00:42:24,542 --> 00:42:26,587
Okay. Fine.

1027
00:42:26,631 --> 00:42:28,458
We can stay.

1028
00:42:28,502 --> 00:42:32,550
But just for
a little while.

1029
00:42:32,593 --> 00:42:35,727
Pick the pieces you want
